data.description:
Lovely 3 bedroom end unit townhome which features a spacious living and dining combo, open kitchen, lots of storage, screened back porch, and a fenced backyard.  HVAC was installed in 2023, new electric panel.

This property offers a wonderful combination of functionality, charm, and investment potential. 

Schedule a showing today and discover the possibilities that await you in this great older townhome with no HOA fees.

It's time to make this house your home or a valuable addition to your investment portfolio.

Seller requires all offers to be accompanied by a current loan approval or proof of funds letter.
